      "heading": "Equation in figure caption.",
      "text": "<p>The normalised background signal is computed as <math><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\"><mtable columnspacing=\"0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em\" displaystyle=\"true\" rowspacing=\"3pt\"><mtr><mtd><msub><mtext>TransformedCommonBackground</mtext><mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\"><mi>i</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>reference</mtext></mrow></msub></mtd><mtd><mi/><mo>=</mo><mtext>max</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msub><mtext>CommonBackground</mtext><mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\"><mi>i</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>reference</mtext></mrow></msub></mrow><mrow><munder><mo form=\"prefix\" movablelimits=\"true\">min</mo><mi>i</mi></munder><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mtext>CommonBackground</mtext><mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\"><mi>i</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>reference</mtext></mrow></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mtd></mtr></mtable></mstyle></math> where the denominator represents the minimum observed background across all samples in the reference cohort, ensuring the transformed values are always non-negative and comparable across experiments. <math><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\"><mtable columnspacing=\"0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em 2em 0em\" displaystyle=\"true\" rowspacing=\"3pt\"><mtr><mtd><msub><mtext>TransformedCommonBackground</mtext><mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\"><mi>i</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>reference</mtext></mrow></msub></mtd><mtd><mi/><mo>=</mo><mtext>max</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msub><mtext>CommonBackground</mtext><mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\"><mi>i</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>reference</mtext></mrow></msub></mrow><mrow><munder><mo form=\"prefix\" movablelimits=\"true\">min</mo><mi>i</mi></munder><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mtext>CommonBackground</mtext><mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\"><mi>i</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>reference</mtext></mrow></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mtd></mtr></mtable></mstyle></math></p>"
